      "title": "India should be alert about unruly behavior of lumpen elements in SL-Swamy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Indian ruling party politician Subramanian Swamy says India should be alert about unruly behavior of lumpen elements in Sri Lanka.",
        "He tweeted ,\u201dAfter getting information that the unruly crowds roaming around Colombo are being guided by SL version of Naxals, Jehadis, anti- socials etc ., India has to be concerned about Sri Lanka\u2019s degeneration caused by lumpen elements, and its future impact on India.\u201d"
